This paper deals with type systems and verification, which are core topics in programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). It also discusses the use of relational refinements and effects, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper touches on security and privacy concerns, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
